snippet.title: WE WERE HERE Xbox One Release Trailer (2019) OFFICIAL HD
snippet.description:
We Were Here is a cooperative first-person puzzle game where you and a friend find yourselves split up inside a sinister castle in the wastes of Antarctica. With only your walkie-talkies and you wits, can you find a way out?

Available now on the Microsoft Store, and playable free for all Xbox Live Gold members September 16 - October 15 2019! 

https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/we-were-here/9p695v9561vb

#Coop #Puzzle #EscapeRoom
